# Contributing to {{ app_name_title }}

## Git Flow

```
main     ← Stable releases
develop  ← Features in progress
feat/*   ← New features
hotfix/* ← Urgent fixes
```

## Pull Request Checklist

- [ ] Tests pass (`pytest`)
- [ ] Coverage 85%+ (`pytest --cov`)
- [ ] Code formatted (`black .`)
- [ ] Linting passes (`ruff check .`)
- [ ] Type checking (`mypy {{ app_name }}`)
- [ ] SECURITY.md updated if needed
- [ ] CHANGELOG.md updated

## Local Development

```bash
# Setup
git clone <repo>
cd {{ app_name }}
pip install -e ".[dev]"
pre-commit install

# Run tests
pytest

# Format code
black .
ruff check --fix .

# Type check
mypy {{ app_name }}
```

## Code Style

- Follow PEP 8
- Use type hints
- Write docstrings (Google style)
- Keep functions small and focused

## Commit Messages

```
feat: Add new feature
fix: Fix bug
docs: Update documentation
test: Add tests
refactor: Refactor code
style: Format code
```

